summary:
Skip the character-making process and begin the adventure at the very doorstep of High Hrothgar.

A blank Nord playable character. Customize to your own liking.
descriptionHtml:
Disclaimer: 

This is my first uploaded file, so I may not be able to help you with some issues. (I\'ll still try, though! If you have a question, a request, feel free to ask!)
I am not the creator of any custom content shown in the pictures.

The appearance of the character will change according to your graphics settings, installed game modifications and custom content. For the best utility of this save, I recommend using character enhancement mods. If you have no mods installed, the result may look quite different from the pictures.


How to install: 

Unzip the file and place it in Documents/My Games/Skyrim/Saves, then load in-game.
author: Annymosa
